{
  "texts": [
    "2024].7.1.3 Dialect identification as an auxiliary task.",
    ": Multi-task learning is used to train models for multiple tasks.",
    "Dialect identification could be used as one of the tasks in order to train equitable models.",
    "Lent et al. [2024] present a multi-task, multi-lingual dataset of Creole languages.",
    "They report the baseline performance of NLU and MT tasks on the dataset using appropriate models."
  ]
}